<MELItem itemNbr="32-32-03" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-32-32-03.1.2-32-32-03">
<Title>Main Gear Side Brace Downlock Springs</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="B" nbrInstalled="8" nbrRequired="6">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One inner or one outer coil spring may be broken or missing from one downlock spring assembly on each main gear side brace.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceNote>
<Para>Each main landing gear side brace includes two downlock spring assemblies.  Each downlock spring assembly incorporates a nested pair of coil springs.  Only one spring may be broken or missing on each side brace.</Para>
</MaintenanceNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
